    <title>济南</title>
    <url>/love-page/2023/03/12/%E6%B5%8E%E5%8D%97/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>2023年3月5号，到济南找jjy。jjy没有出来和我住，我就住在学校外面。</p>
<p>我们第一天去了恒隆广场，在附近买了小柿子耳夹35但是在1688上只卖几块钱，我们感觉自己又做了大冤种。</p>
<p><img src="/love-page/assets/4AC8DF1B82DA18C9F0D7F5B5F313C318.jpg" alt="晚上在兴隆山 戴小柿子耳夹的jjy"><br><img src="/love-page/assets/506AF855FB12BB753388741DF906976E.jpg" alt="晚上在兴隆山"><br><img src="/love-page/assets/FED8A65316C9E87DC41C840BD025EF43.jpg" alt="晚上在兴隆山"><br><img src="/love-page/assets/IMG_20230305_133725.jpg" alt="一辆拉风的五菱"><br>本来当天想去趵突泉逛逛，可是没有票了，拍了拍护城河<br><img src="/love-page/assets/IMG_20230305_144006.jpg" alt="济南护城河"></p>
<p>第二天我们去了趵突泉，在趵突泉校区吃了饭，感觉比青岛校区的食堂好吃一点。<br><img src="/love-page/assets/3972AAE5205DDA8508FA5374A3D594C0.jpg" alt="游趵突泉"></p>
<p><img src="/love-page/assets/2851B2B0E26D95D6F373DF040ED109BB.jpg" alt="游趵突泉"><br><img src="/love-page/assets/4738BAEB73D7532CF0A30DF08445B2CA.jpg" alt="游趵突泉"><br><img src="/love-page/assets/IMG_20230306_110415.jpg" alt="游趵突泉"></p>
<p><img src="/love-page/assets/IMG_20230306_111027.jpg" alt="游趵突泉"><br><img src="/love-page/assets/IMG_20230306_113120.jpg" alt="jjy说是美女与保镖"><br><img src="/love-page/assets/MTXX_MH20230306_194451071.jpg" alt="游趵突泉"><br><img src="/love-page/assets/C76B6C8BC06858DA911C7C82237551B4.jpg" alt="曲水亭街一角"><br><img src="/love-page/assets/D3109C35E2827AA2DD5EDFED336DC4D5.jpg" alt="游趵突泉"><br><img src="/love-page/assets/6F8D6605F236CED3105AAD863991EF2D.jpg" alt="游趵突泉"></p>
]]></content>
